<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idef81a423-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s2372"><num value="2372">§ 2372.</num><heading> Payment of plant variety protection fees; return of excess amounts</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">All fees shall be paid to the Secretary, and the Secretary may refund any sum paid by mistake or in excess of the fee required.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idef81a424-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/91/577/tI/s32">Pub. L. 91–577, title I, § 32</ref>, <date date="1970-12-24">Dec. 24, 1970</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/84/1545">84 Stat. 1545</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
